Please keep checking your email for updates.
</p>

<!-- BUTTONS -->
<div class="mt-6 space-y-3">

<a href="/jobs"
class="block bg-indigo-600 text-white py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-indigo-500 transition">
Browse More Jobs
</a>

<a href="/user-dashboard"
class="block border border-gray-300 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100 transition">
Go to Dashboard
</a>

